  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1402900/extras/8e6fcb50e57449571b1afa26e4485d14.avif?t=1773407513\" width=616 height=85 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Twilight Memoria: Sun and Moon</i> is a nostalgic RPG about growing up in a seemingly quiet village, one that you soon discover is full of secrets. You play as two inseparable childhood friends: Rucifar Demien, the spirited son of a famous adventurer, and Luna Silver, a prodigy in alchemy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1402900/extras/0be79353cbaaad6d0dc15ffff0f85af2.poster.avif?t=1773407513\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1402900/extras/0be79353cbaaad6d0dc15ffff0f85af2.webm?t=1773407513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1402900/extras/0be79353cbaaad6d0dc15ffff0f85af2.mp4?t=1773407513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Instead of idling away your days, you’ll help villagers, take on requests from the village chief, and uncover the strange mysteries unfolding around you. As Rucifar and Luna’s bond deepens, you’ll begin to explore the unfamiliar feelings of first love, a step into a new world of romance, friendship, and self-discovery.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Through heartfelt interactions, meaningful alchemy choices, and a story filled with warmth and wonder, Sun and Moon captures the spirit of childhood adventures, quiet acts of heroism, and the innocence of falling in love for the very first time.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1402900/extras/fb44cc5c8baa7233e6e4592a42397054.avif?t=1773407513\" width=616 height=85 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Real-Time Turn-Based Combat</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle monsters using an Active Time Battle system where every character, including enemies, acts on their own timer. Rucifar fights on the front lines while Luna supports from behind, healing, crafting bombs, and using items mid-battle. You’ll need quick thinking and teamwork to survive, especially since you're just two kids up against dangerous creatures.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1402900/extras/89e9e6294d13ece26c2a25b70f697676.poster.avif?t=1773407513\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1402900/extras/89e9e6294d13ece26c2a25b70f697676.webm?t=1773407513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1402900/extras/89e9e6294d13ece26c2a25b70f697676.mp4?t=1773407513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unpredictable Alchemy System</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Recreate the joy of mixing wild potions as a kid, throwing in whatever you had and hoping for magic. Craft potions, bombs, and quest items using a flexible ingredient system where recipes only list types, like \"Liquid\" or \"Leaf.\" It’s up to you whether you choose spring water… or monster blood. Every choice affects the outcome, making experimentation part of the adventure!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Quest-Based Village Life</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help your neighbors and prove your worth by completing requests from the village chief. From gathering materials to investigating strange happenings, each quest deepens your connection to the community.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1402900/extras/0d6004158fb4679187cb8d4bb331d622.poster.avif?t=1773407513\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1402900/extras/0d6004158fb4679187cb8d4bb331d622.webm?t=1773407513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1402900/extras/0d6004158fb4679187cb8d4bb331d622.mp4?t=1773407513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A Story of Friendship and First Love</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grow alongside Rucifar and Luna as they support each other, challenge expectations, and experience the confusing thrill of first love. Strengthen their bond through shared adventures, meaningful choices, and quiet moments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1402900/extras/e3bd68d22112b783c636c8fe23cbfdfa.poster.avif?t=1773407513\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1402900/extras/e3bd68d22112b783c636c8fe23cbfdfa.webm?t=1773407513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1402900/extras/e3bd68d22112b783c636c8fe23cbfdfa.mp4?t=1773407513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1402900/extras/8e6fcb50e57449571b1afa26e4485d14.avif?t=1773407513\" width=616 height=85 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Twilight Memoria: Sun and Moon</i> is a nostalgic RPG about growing up in a seemingly quiet village, one that you soon discover is full of secrets. You play as two inseparable childhood friends: Rucifar Demien, the spirited son of a famous adventurer, and Luna Silver, a prodigy in alchemy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1402900/extras/0be79353cbaaad6d0dc15ffff0f85af2.poster.avif?t=1773407513\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1402900/extras/0be79353cbaaad6d0dc15ffff0f85af2.webm?t=1773407513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1402900/extras/0be79353cbaaad6d0dc15ffff0f85af2.mp4?t=1773407513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Instead of idling away your days, you’ll help villagers, take on requests from the village chief, and uncover the strange mysteries unfolding around you. As Rucifar and Luna’s bond deepens, you’ll begin to explore the unfamiliar feelings of first love, a step into a new world of romance, friendship, and self-discovery.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Through heartfelt interactions, meaningful alchemy choices, and a story filled with warmth and wonder, Sun and Moon captures the spirit of childhood adventures, quiet acts of heroism, and the innocence of falling in love for the very first time.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: cent