e your worth by completing requests from the village chief. From gathering materials to investigating strange happenings, each quest deepens your connection to the community.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1402900/extras/0d6004158fb4679187cb8d4bb331d622.poster.avif?t=1773407513\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1402900/extras/0d6004158fb4679187cb8d4bb331d622.webm?t=1773407513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1402900/extras/0d6004158fb4679187cb8d4bb331d622.mp4?t=1773407513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A Story of Friendship and First Love</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grow alongside Rucifar and Luna as they support each other, challenge expectations, and experience the confusing thrill of first love. Strengthen their bond through shared adventures, meaningful choices, and quiet moments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1402900/extras/e3bd68d22112b783c636c8fe23cbfdfa.poster.avif?t=1773407513\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1402900/extras/e3bd68d22112b783c636c8fe23cbfdfa.webm?t=1773407513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1402900/extras/e3bd68d22112b783c636c8fe23cbfdfa.mp4?t=1773407513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2>",
